      <p>
        Choose from our diverse fleet including pickup trucks, box trucks,
        flatbeds, and cargo vans. Each vehicle is meticulously maintained,
        regularly inspected, and equipped with modern safety features to ensure
        a reliable rental experience every time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Trusted by Thousands</h2>
      <p>
        Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust TruckRiser for their
        moving, delivery, and logistics needs. Our 4.8-star rating reflects our
        commitment to reliability, transparent pricing, and exceptional customer
        service on every rental.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

